XAdES Signature Facet. Implements XAdES v1.4.1 which is compatible with XAdES v1.3.2. The implemented XAdES format is XAdES-BES/EPES. It's up to another part of the signature service to upgrade the XAdES-BES to a XAdES-X-L.
This implementation has been tested against an implementation that participated multiple ETSI XAdES plugtests.
@author Frank Cornelis @see XAdES

